  <official_title>Intra-Articular Injection of Etanercept in Patient Suffering From Rheumatoid Arthritis : a Double-Blind Randomized Study for Evaluation of Efficacy and Safety of Etanercept Versus Intra-Articular Steroid Injection in Acute Synovitis</official_title>
